2026-06-01T11:10:25.1147888Z 275            stale Intent. The library's onCreate reads the PendingIntent
2026-06-01T11:10:25.1148655Z 276            extra without null-checking; if Android recreates the activity
2026-06-01T11:10:25.1148866Z 277            and the extra is missing, it NPEs on
2026-06-01T11:10:25.1149233Z 278            PendingIntent.getIntentSender(). noHistory + excludeFromRecents
2026-06-01T11:10:25.1149552Z 279            finishes the activity as soon as it leaves the foreground so it
2026-06-01T11:10:25.1149853Z 280            is never re-entered with a missing extra. Library 8.x adds its
2026-06-01T11:10:25.1150153Z 281            own configChanges absorber and a v2 proxy, both of which we
